    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>试玩版完整提供游戏前两章节的内容，支持深度体验、尽情探索。现在率领你的四人英雄小队开启征程。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/f1161f462e8c79e58f230b69f47c26e1.avif?t=1771853101\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>引领、适应、生存</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎踏上 Valor of Man 的冒险征程。这款融合Roguelite元素的回合制策略RPG将带你走进一个充斥着毁灭与启示的破碎之地。从 12 个独特职业中挑选英雄，组建你的四人小队，每种职业都拥有鲜明的定位与独特战斗风格。掌握协同作战的艺术，深入探索超过700种技能、道具及改变战局的圣物。打造专属你的战术体系，迎接即将到来的严酷试炼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/37f49363a870399c3014f1a9acd9353d.poster.avif?t=1771853101\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/37f49363a870399c3014f1a9acd9353d.webm?t=1771853101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/37f49363a870399c3014f1a9acd9353d.mp4?t=1771853101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态战斗系统，战机稍纵即逝</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏战斗玩法基于DND系统设计，敌人随时可能对你的攻击和移动做出反应，每次行动都是对策略与运气的综合考验。在有限的回合行动点数中，利用英雄技能与道具制造强大的连携组合效果，找准最佳时机，释放毁灭性伤害，给予关键敌人致命一击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/e121a029f032d7b2e4e032462e0ef8d5.poster.avif?t=1771853101\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/e121a029f032d7b2e4e032462e0ef8d5.webm?t=1771853101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/e121a029f032d7b2e4e032462e0ef8d5.mp4?t=1771853101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解锁圣物与能力，直面挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强力技能、武器装备和带有特殊效果的圣物将随着冒险深入不断解锁。在10个愈发残酷的关卡中磨砺自己、不断成长。Roguelite式旅程中，死亡并非终点，而是通往精进与征服的必经之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/0468d6610d1e931dde0f62db6d2f04a2.poster.avif?t=1771853101\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/0468d6610d1e931dde0f62db6d2f04a2.webm?t=1771853101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/0468d6610d1e931dde0f62db6d2f04a2.mp4?t=1771853101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无限重玩，无尽探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每场旅程结束，都将为下一次冒险带来新的内容，积累更多成功可能性。Valor of Man 提供丰富的可解锁和重玩内容，无论你热衷策略、渴望挑战，还是沉迷于世界背后的传说与秘密，都总是能在再次启程后发现新的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/d1ee7b78ed36ff6ad222a80a970990b9.poster.avif?t=1771853101\" width=1170 height=548 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/d1ee7b78ed36ff6ad222a80a970990b9.webm?t=1771853101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222870/extras/d1ee7b78ed36ff6ad222a80a970990b9.mp4?t=1771853101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在就试玩并将Valor of Man加入愿望单，响应命运召唤，提前踏上冒险之旅吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >策略桌游风格融入roguelite元素，专为重复游玩设计</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特动态战斗系统，战局随每次攻击改变</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版包含300+技能、290件装备、170件圣物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+种独特敌人与9场专属Boss战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10大难度逐级递进的关卡可供挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版支持手柄与Steam Deck</p></li></ul>",
